@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cptfhh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp((0.82 / tmp))
    v0 = wp.sin((v0 - (tmp + 0.19 - v1 + 0.17)))
    v0 = v0
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.sin(tmp + 0.35) / tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
